data.description: Welcome to your dream ranch-style home nestled on a picturesque 1.23-acre lot, open to all the possibilities you can dream up! This spacious residence boasts four bedrooms, providing ample space for both family and guests. The primary suite, complete with its own ensuite bathroom, offers a private oasis for relaxation and comfort. The heart of this home lies in its well-designed layout, featuring a convenient first-floor laundry room that adds a touch of practicality to your daily routine. Imagine the ease and efficiency of handling laundry tasks without the need to navigate stairs. Car enthusiasts and hobbyists alike will appreciate the oversized two-car garage, providing not only shelter for your vehicles but also offering additional storage space or a workshop area. The possibilities are endless! Descend into the sprawling basement, a versatile space that comes with a private entrance, opening up exciting opportunities for customization. Whether you envision a home office, a recreation room, or even a separate living area for guests or extended family, this basement is a blank canvas awaiting your personal touch. As you step outside, the expansive 1.23-acre lot beckons with its potential for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply enjoying the tranquility of nature. The surrounding landscape provides a peaceful retreat, creating a harmonious blend of privacy and open space. Don't miss the chance to make this ranch-style haven your own. Schedule a tour today and discover the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and versatility in this home on 1.23 acres. NEW ROOF MAY 2023~!
